        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>What is the best book you've ever read and why?</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 80 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>Oh, my best book? Well, to be honnest, I don't read at all. I don't know why but I can't spend my time reading books, I fell it like a waste of time... it's not funny because I want to read, the Lovecraft's novels seems to be very good for me, for my imagination maybe. Now I don't know what to write for you, maybe a story?</p>
                <p>Once upon a time... no just kidding, i'm a funny guy hu?</p>
                <p>Okay, now the eighty words will be complete, or not? So many questions and no answers...</p>
            </div>
